data.message: Attempted 100% match of glassmorphism card - discovered layout axis error: Created multiple iterations but had circles on diagonal axis (corners) instead of vertical axis (center top/bottom). Learned that fundamental placement assumptions must be verified before fine-tuning coordinates. The 800x800 frame size and element proportions were correct, but circle x-positions were wrong throughout.
